name: Darkness
description: This work shows the different attitudes of people towards darkness. For some, darkness is a very comfortable place where they feel peaceful, this calmness and comfort is embodied by a beautiful and gentle woman's face. For other people, darkness is something dangerous and sometimes terrible, the mind draws various bizarre forms that cause horror, remember your childhood. Horror is represented by a red and creepy inhuman eye. In this work, a person will first of all see what is closer to his liking, in the depths of our subconsciousness the most honest attitude to darkness is hidden and no matter how we want, we cannot hide it. But what cannot be changed is that the darkness is mesmerizing.
